llie Holiday |location=Gloucestershire, England |publisher=Spellmount Publishers |isbn=0-946771-05-7 |url=https://archive.org/details/billieholiday00jame }}\n* {{Cite news| last = Kaplan | first = Samuel W. | year = February 2002 | title = Strange Fruit | journal = [[Humanity & Society]] | volume = Volume 26, No. 1 | pages = 77\u201383}}\n* {{Cite video |last = Katz | first = Joel | year = 2002 | title =California Newsreel: Strange Fruit}}\n* {{Cite book |last=Millar |first=Jack |year=1994 |title=Fine and Mellow: A Discography of Billie Holiday |location=London |publisher=Billie Holiday Circle |isbn=1-899161-00-7}}\n* {{Cite book |last=Nicholson |first=Stuart |year=1995 |title=Billie Holiday |location=Boston |publisher=Northeastern University Press |isbn=1-55553-303-5}}\n* {{Cite book |last=O'Meally |first=Robert |year=1991 |title=Lady Day: The Many Faces of Billie Holiday |location=New York |publisher=Da Capo Press |isbn=978-0-306-80959-0 |oclc=45009756|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book | title=Understanding Cultural Policy | first1=Carole | last1=Rosenstein | publisher=Routledge | year=2018 | isbn=9781315526836 | page=134 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YHhQDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT134 | ref=harv }}</ref>\n* {{Cite book|last=Szwed|first=John|authorlink=John Szwed|year=2015|title=Billie Holiday: The Musician and The Myth|location=New York|publisher=Viking|isbn=978-0670014729|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/billieholidaymus0000szwe}}\n\n==Further reading==\n*{{cite news|last1=Chow|first1=Andrew R.|title=Billie Holiday, via Hologram, Returning to the Apollo|url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/09/09/billie-holiday-hologram-to-debut-at-apollo-this-year/?module=WatchingPortal&region=c-column-middle-span-region&pgType=Homepage&action=click&mediaId=wide&state=standard&contentPlacement=8&version=internal&contentCollection=artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com&contentId=http%3A%2F%2Fartsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com%2F2015%2F09%2F09%2Fbillie-holiday-hologram-to-debut-at-a