\u00edaz''']] (born 1959)\n*[[File:Flag of Spain.svg|25px|Spain]] [[Fernando Fern\u00e1n G\u00f3mez|Fernando '''Fern\u00e1n G\u00f3mez''']] (born 1921)\n*[[File:Flag of Cuba.svg|25px|Cuba]] [[Andy Garc\u00eda|Andy '''Garc\u00eda''']] (born 1956)\n*[[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Gael Garc\u00eda Bernal|Gael '''Garc\u00eda Bernal''']] (born 1978)\n*[[File:Flag of Spain.svg|25px|Spain]] [[Sancho Gracia|Sancho '''Gracia''']] (born 1936)\n*[[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Salma Hayek|Salma '''Hayek''']] (born 1966)\n*[[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Pedro Infante|Pedro '''Infante''']] (1917\u20131957)\n*[[File:Flag of Puerto Rico.svg|25px|Puerto Rico]] [[Ra\u00fal Juli\u00e1|Ra\u00fal '''Juli\u00e1''']] (1940\u20131994)\n*[[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Katy Jurado|Katy '''Jurado''']] (1924\u20132002)\n*[[File:Flag of Argentina.svg|25px|Argentina]] [[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Libertad Lamarque|Libertad '''Lamarque''']] (1908\u20132000)\n*[[File:Flag of Colombia.svg|25px|Colombia]] [[John Leguizamo|John '''Leguizamo''']] (born 1964)\n*[[File:Flag of the United States.svg|25px|United States]] [[George Lopez|George '''Lopez''']] (born 1961)\n*[[File:Flag of the United States.svg|25px|United States]] [[Eva Longoria|Eva '''Longoria''']] (born 1975)\n*[[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Diego Luna|Diego '''Luna''']] (born 1979)\n*[[File:Flag of Argentina.svg|25px|Argentina]] [[Federico Luppi|Federico '''Luppi''']] (born 1936)\n*[[File:Flag of the United States.svg|25px|United States]] [[Cheech Marin|Cheech '''Marin''']] (born 1946)\n*[[File:Flag of the United States.svg|25px|United States]] [[Eva Mendes|Eva '''Mendes''']] (born 1974)\n*[[File:Flag of Spain.svg|25px|Spain]] [[Jordi Moll\u00e1|Jordi '''Moll\u00e1''']] (born 1968)\n*[[File:Flag of Mexico.svg|25px|Mexico]] [[Ricardo Montalb\u00e1n|Ricardo '''Montalb\u00e1n''']] (1921\u20132009)\n*[[File:Flag of Spain.svg|25px|Spain]] [[Sara Montiel|Sara '''Montiel''']] (bo